  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Create a bubble plot to explore the relationship between yearly compensation (`ConvertedCompYearly`) and job satisfaction (`JobSatPoints_6`), with bubble size representing age.\n"
